not where it needs to be to
entice companies
to want to come here.

22:23.809 --> 22:28.514 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KAI RYSSDAL: So, Bobby Kennedy
comes here
in 1967, right, almost 50 years
ago.

22:28.614 --> 22:30.249 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JIMMY WILSON: Yes.

22:30.349 --> 22:32.818 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
KAI RYSSDAL: Has it been wasted
time?

22:32.918 --> 22:34.920 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JIMMY WILSON: Has been wasted
