She'd like to see freedom
village become a

22:38.824 --> 22:40.392 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
place to help those in need.

22:40.492 --> 22:43.896 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CATHERINE WILSON: I ain't given
up Freedom
Village. I still believe.

22:43.996 --> 22:52.171 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
KAI RYSSDAL: For the "PBS
