22:52.271 --> 23:00.579 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Stay with us.

23:00.679 --> 23:06.352 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Coming up on the "NewsHour":
what top executive
Roger Ailes' sudden departure
from FOX News

23:06.452 --> 23:11.390 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
means for the world of
television; and Mark
Shields and David Brooks give
